Nuance
------

*Hugo Barra, welcome to Stratechery.*

*Hugo Barra:* Thank you, Ben. Thanks for having me.

*I was inspired to reach out to you for a Stratechery Interview because of =
a really fantastic blog post you wrote ( https://hugo.blog/2024/03/11/visio=
n-pro/ ) about the Apple Vision Pro ( https://stratechery.com/2024/the-appl=
